{"at":1772691643575,"data":{"id":5388173,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nguyễn Hùng","primary":true}}]}},"person_5657273_translations":{"at":1772691644485,"data":{"id":5657273,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kiran Krishnakumar","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Киран Кришнакумар","primary":false}}]}},"person_128628_translations":{"at":1772691657094,"data":{"id":128628,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Susan Scott \"Scottie\" Thompson (born November 9, 1981, height 5' 7\" (1,70 m)) is an American film, television and stage actress.\n\nThompson grew up in Richmond, Virginia, where she attended Collegiate School. From an early age she began learning ballet, jazz and modern dance. She danced with the Richmond Ballet for many years, took a year off after graduating to dance with the company, and then went on to study for a degree in Performance Studies and Literature at Harvard University. Thompson started dancing with the Harvard Ballet Company and acted in many theater productions. She was the publicity manager for the Hasty Pudding Theatricals in 2003, worked for Let's Go Travel Guides, and was credited as associate editor for the travel book Let's Go: Vietnam. Thompson graduated in 2005 with a bachelor's degree in Performance Studies and Literature, focusing on French and Postcolonial works.","name":"Scottie Thompson","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SE","iso_639_1":"sv","name":"svenska","english_name":"Swedish","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"AT","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"Susan Scott “Scottie” Thompson（1981 年 11 月 9 日出生，身高 5 英尺 7 英寸（1,70 米））是美国电影、电视和舞台女演员。\n\n汤普森在弗吉尼亚州里士满长大，在那里她就读于大学学校。她从小就开始学习芭蕾舞、爵士舞和现代舞。她在里士满芭蕾舞团跳舞多年，毕业后休学一年，与舞团一起跳舞，然后继续在哈佛大学攻读表演研究和文学学位。汤普森开始在哈佛芭蕾舞团跳舞，并出演了许多戏剧作品。她是2003年Hasty Pudding Theatricals的宣传经理，为Let's Go Travel Guides工作，并被认为是旅行书Let's Go：越南的副主编。汤普森于2005年毕业，获得表演研究和文学学士学位，专注于法国和后殖民作品。","name":"斯考蒂·汤姆森","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"Susan Scott “Scottie” Thompson（1981 年 11 月 9 日出生，身高 5 英尺 7 英寸（1, 70 米））是美國電影、電視和舞台女演員。\n\n湯普森在弗吉尼亞州裏士滿長大，在那裏她就讀於大學學校。她從小就開始學習芭蕾舞、爵士舞和現代舞。她在裏士滿芭蕾舞團跳舞多年，畢業後休學一年，與舞團一起跳舞，然後繼續在哈佛大學攻讀表演研究和文學學位。湯普森開始在哈佛芭蕾舞團跳舞，並出演了許多戲劇作品。她是 2003 年 Hasty Pudding Theatricals 的宣傳經理，為 Let's Go Travel Guides 工作，並被認為是旅行書 Let's Go：越南的副主編。湯普森於 2005 年畢業，獲得表演研究和文學學士學位，專注於法國和後殖民作品。","name":"斯考蒂·湯姆森","primary":false}}]}},"person_4816116_translations":{"at":1772691668111,"data":{"id":4816116,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"刘浏，原名刘浩河，女，河北省石家庄市人，中国配音演员。其配音作品涵盖动画电影及电视剧领域，2015年参与动画电影《天眼传奇》《咕噜咕噜美人鱼》配音工作。2017年，刘浏为电视剧《快递先生与贵妃小姐》进行配音。2023年担任电视剧《长相思》中小鱼角色的配音。","name":"刘浏","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"劉瀏","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Liu Liu","primary":false}}]}},"tv_109989_keywords":{"at":1772691669047,"data":{"id":109989,"results":[{"name":"crime investigation","id":189402},{"name":"modern drama","id":319157}]}}}}